videos.headline: Vols score TD on blocked punt
videos.description: Tennessee's Marquill Osborne blocks East Tennessee's punt and runs it into the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Thompson's interception sets up Vols' TD
videos.description: Bryce Thompson intercepts East Tennessee State QB Logan Marchi and returns it to the ETS 1-yard line.

videos.headline: Vols WR Murphy easily scores 50-yard TD
videos.description: Tennessee QB Keller Chryst connects with wide-open WR Jordan Murphy for a 50-yard pass.
